  "summary": {
    "brief": "Richard W. Gannett v. Richard Neumeier, Morrison Mahoney LLP, Minnesota Lawyers Mutual Insurance Company, Molly Eiden and Mel L. Greenberg. Medical malpractice case involving paediatrics.",
